Why does everything have to include a supervillain team?  Why do
hero weddings also have to involve combats?  (Oh, for the
Terry/Donna Troy wedding in Teen Titans, many years ago.) Why do
special-event books always have way too many costumes?  Suitable
only for those whose tastes incline towards the above.

Brenda

